-- MOVES-Miton Group appoints Andrew Mellis regional sales manager
-- 
-- Wed Dec 03, 2014 05:13AM EST
-- None



Dec 3 (Reuters) - Asset manager Miton Group Plc <MGRM.L> appointed Andrew Mellis regional sales manager, effective Jan. 5 next year.

Mellis will cover accounts across London and the southeast of England, including East Anglia, the company said.  Most recently, he was business development manager at London & Capital.